'''Shaper headdresses''' were special headdresses worn by members of the [[Shaper caste]] of the [[Yuuzhan Vong]]. Headdresses had snake like appendages growing out of them, and had a rudimentary connection to the Shaper's mental state. Shaper headdresses could take various forms, usually linking together into a ball (giving an appearance similar to the turbans used by the [[Intendant caste]]) or would simply stick out (making them look similar to [[Ho'Din/Legends|Ho'Dins]]).

